{"tid":832334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★越南女涉撻手機　遭途人制服扯爛衫褲","createTime":"2018-09-22T16:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T14:45:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b24c7b167fa2931ddf58b39dbdf299c30441513","tid":832334,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180922/photo/bkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180923000045\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180922%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180923000045&h=c3708ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180922/photo/bkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180923000045\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180922%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180923000045&h=1a4b43fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長沙灣發生店舖扒竊案，今午(22日)4時許，一名姓袁(35歲)女子報案，指在長沙灣青山道666號一間店舖，遭一名非華裔女子偷去手袋內一部約值8000港元的手機。警方接報到場，期間該名持有香港身份證的45歲越南女子情緒激動，警員隨即把她制服，並在其手袋內，檢獲屬於受害人的電話及另外兩部手機。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌扒竊拘捕該名越南女子，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進，正調查她是否與其他盜竊案有關。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者吳小姐指，當時她在對面香港工業中心逛街，期間一名中年女子疑偷手機，有店舖職員及市民發現追出，該可疑女子沿商場出口逃走，期間更匿藏在貨車底，最後被職員及途人合力拉出，喝令她交出手機。<br />\n<br />\n糾纏間，可疑女子的衫褲被扯爛，<span style=\"color: red;\">露出胸圍及底褲</span>，期間圍觀的途人眾多，女子在警員到場後，堅稱「自己冇偷電話」，又投訴遭人毆打。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180922/bkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180922%2Fbkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001.html&d=czK%2FpXY%2BwmSUs%2FbpWp5dOdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d0d8db3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180922/bkn-20180922203427357-0922_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75cf978c4c3fa9e146d152a1d24261db1ad72bbe","tid":832334,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n部電話係咪會比人拎去做證物，幾個月都冇得用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b85aaa1af6115b2f759cc67b23326ac2bce110c","tid":832334,"uid":129658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"咁爽快有相已經知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb512ca79d7afb40b623b9b58e6604da21ef8f1b","tid":832334,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0204a17a2412106e9695caf8aaaef4902452512e","tid":832334,"uid":75521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"Cls"}]}